data.description: Charming 4-sided brick home has been freshly painted outside and is located in a quiet neighborhood just minutes from downtown Griffin. This move in ready home features new HVAC, newer furnace, new gas stove will be installed before closing, newer roof, newer water heater, built in bookshelves, original hard wood floors under the carpet, tile bathroom and lots of storage in the attic. Outside includes a large deck, covered porch and fenced in private back yard. Home is being sold" as is". The seller is a licensed real estate agent in Florida.
